<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 13 Mar 2026 01:04:32 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>加密货币交易所押注预测市场以度过熊市</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-12/crypto-exchanges-eye-prediction-markets-stock-trading-to-survive-bear-market</link><description>要么做大，要么回家。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iyP5aCxFbnMw/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-12/crypto-exchanges-eye-prediction-markets-stock-trading-to-survive-bear-market</guid></item><item><title>Tether Investment 首席执行官在主导交易热潮后辞职</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-12/tether-investments-chief-to-step-down-after-leading-deals-spree</link><description>Tether Holdings SA 首席投资官理查德·希思科特 (Richard Heathcote) 负责监督支持其主要稳定币的巨额储备，以及涉及从足球俱乐部到人形机器人等各种领域的交易热潮，他即将辞去职务。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iFyR5_uXgrOs/v0/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 18:44:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-12/tether-investments-chief-to-step-down-after-leading-deals-spree</guid></item><item><title>伊朗战争导致油价飙升至 100 美元以上，比特币走弱</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-12/bitcoin-weakens-as-oil-surges-back-above-100-on-iran-war</link><description>由于对伊朗冲突的担忧加深，油价短暂回升至每桶 100 美元以上，比特币波动接近近期价格水平。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/imyQrgW3agvE/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 04:20:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-12/bitcoin-weakens-as-oil-surges-back-above-100-on-iran-war</guid></item><item><title>尽管IPO规模达数十亿美元，但SPAC却很少有公司上市</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-11/spacs-take-few-companies-public-despite-11-7-billion-ipo-haul</link><description>在今年筹集了 117 亿美元资金的一系列 IPO 之后，一批新的空白支票公司加入了长队：所有其他工具都在等待将公司上市的机会。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ixKeTsNsxp.U/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Mar 2026 16:33:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-11/spacs-take-few-companies-public-despite-11-7-billion-ipo-haul</guid></item><item><title>Circle、币安加入万事达卡加密货币合作伙伴计划</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-11/circle-binance-join-mastercard-s-crypto-partner-program</link><description>万事达卡公司正在招募超过 85 家数字资产公司、支付提供商和金融机构，包括 Circle Internet Group Inc.、Binance 和 Gemini Space Station Inc.，加入一项新的全球合作伙伴计划，该计划旨在将加密支付与其网络保持连接，因为稳定币被宣传为传统支付轨道的替代品。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ioYm_OchNHF4/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Mar 2026 13:56:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-11/circle-binance-join-mastercard-s-crypto-partner-program</guid></item></channel></rss>